Package: chiptsne
Type: Package
Title: Application of t-sne to NGS Genomic Signal Profiles
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: person("Joseph R", "Boyd", email = "jrboyd@uvm.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Supports all stages of analysis of NGS data using t-sne.  This 
    includes data retrieval from .bam and .bigWig files, normalization, running 
    t-sne, figure generation, and interactive analysis.
